OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew diverse Lego toys      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Famazing, says disabled girl
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A disabled girl who wrote to Lego      
OL,6, asking for better representation in    
OL,7, their toys said a new figure with a    
OL,8, limb difference was "amazing".         
OL,10,FEight-year-old Sofia from Sussex was   
OL,11,Fborn without a left hand, and said she 
OL,12,Ffelt unrepresented by the toys.        
OL,14,FThe firm is releasing a new range of   
OL,15,Ftoys featuring diverse characters, and 
OL,16,Fsurprised Sofia with an announcement on
OL,17,FBBC Breakfast.                         
OL,19,FA Lego designer said the new toys were 
OL,20,Fmade "to represent the real world".    
